description:
For an international project in Chennai, we are urgently looking for a remote Azure/.NET Full Stack Developer with REACT. Candidates need to have experience with Azure DevOps.










 We are looking for a motivated contractor. This position is long\\-term. Candidates need to be fluent in English.










**Tasks and responsibilities:** 



* Plan, design, develop, test, and deploy the application;
* Work closely with the project Architect to get approval on the technical solution for each deliverable;
* Document the user stories, technical details, test cases and test results as per the established process;









**Profile:** 



* Bachelor or Master degree;
* \\+5 years of .NET Full Stack experience;
* \\+2 years in Microsoft Azure;
* \\+3 years of experience in Microsoft Web development using ASP.NET, MVC and Web API, should be hands\\-on;
* Experience with Azure DevOps;
* Hands on experience on.NET Core 5\\+;
* Must have experience in development using client\\-side scripting using Typescript with ReactJS 18\\+;
* Hands on experience on Functions and Web Apps, Logic Apps, SQL DB, Azure Storage, Data Factory etc;
* Experience creating Tables, writing stored procedures and queries in SQL Server;
* Working knowledge of Entity Framework or equivalent frameworks;
* Creating, deploying, configuring applications on Azure PaaS;
* Preferably Microsoft Certified Azure Developer and MCSA in Web Applications or MCSD App Builder, Azure Developer Certified and Web Development Certified;
* Experience with client interaction, requirement gathering, architecture planning, designing solution approach, individual contributor/developer;
* Experience with Power BI and Azure Cognitive services will be a plus;
* SAFe Agile training;
* Fluent in English;
